data.text:
King Albert II of Belgium, right, shares a few words with Princess Lea Inga Dora Wohlman of Belgium, second from left, wife of Prince Alexandre of Belgium the halfbrother of King Albert II of Belgium who died on Nov. 29, 2009, aged 67, during the funerals at the church of Laeken in Brussels, Friday Dec. 4, 2009. Second from right is Princess Marie Esmeralda of Belgium, halfsister of King Albert and sister of Prince Alexandre. People at left is unknown. (AP Photo/Thierry Charlier)
